Integration Test  Following the steps on &ldquo;How to build, setting local and docker environment for light-eventuate-4j framework&rdquo;:  To start event store, cdc service, and command/query side service
 Send request from command side the publish events:  From postmand, send post request:
URL: http://localhost:8083/v1/todos;
Headers:[{&ldquo;key&rdquo;:&ldquo;Content-Type&rdquo;,&ldquo;value&rdquo;:&ldquo;application/json&rdquo;,&ldquo;description&rdquo;:&ldquo;&rdquo;}];
Body: {&ldquo;title&rdquo;:&rdquo; this is the test todo from postman1&rdquo;,&ldquo;completed&rdquo;:false,&ldquo;order&rdquo;:0};
Response: { &ldquo;done&rdquo;: true, &ldquo;cancelled&rdquo;: false, &ldquo;completedExceptionally&rdquo;: false, &ldquo;numberOfDependents&rdquo;: 0 };
This request will send request which will call backe-end service to generate a &ldquo;create todo&rdquo; event and publish to event store.
